but will they belittle me as "a pervert"?

268
00:18:35,323 --> 00:18:38,075
Trapped with those numb bastards...

269
00:18:38,659 --> 00:18:40,244
left to rot, with nowhere to go...

270
00:18:42,830 --> 00:18:44,707
I won't let that happen to me.

271
00:18:48,252 --> 00:18:52,256
[laughter]

272
00:18:53,257 --> 00:18:54,550
[Takao] I'm going to do this.

273
00:18:56,427 --> 00:18:59,180
A place that will make Nakamura laugh.

274
00:19:01,641 --> 00:19:03,016
That's going to be...

275
00:19:03,017 --> 00:19:05,477
GIRLS' CHANGING ROOM

276
00:19:05,478 --> 00:19:06,854
"the other side" for me.

277
00:19:12,818 --> 00:19:14,027
[♪ music fades]

278
00:19:14,028 --> 00:19:17,280
[indistinct chatter, laughter]

279
00:19:17,281 --> 00:19:19,449
You guys, my panties are gone.

280
00:19:19,450 --> 00:19:21,284
[girls exclaiming]

281
00:19:21,285 --> 00:19:22,702
[Ai] What? No way.

282
00:19:22,703 --> 00:19:24,079
[girl] Mine are gone, too.

283
00:19:24,080 --> 00:19:26,790
[girls chattering, exclaiming]

284
00:19:26,791 --> 00:19:28,459
Are yours missing, too, Nanako?

285
00:19:29,377 --> 00:19:31,252
What? Yeah.

286
00:19:31,253 --> 00:19:32,921
- [Ai] I wonder who did it.
- [Nanako] Right?

287
00:19:32,922 --> 00:19:33,923
[excited chatter]

288
00:20:00,282 --> 00:20:01,283
I've been waiting.

289
00:20:40,281 --> 00:20:41,574
Nakamura.

290
00:20:42,700 --> 00:20:43,701
This space...

291
00:20:44,869 --> 00:20:45,953
Just this space

292
00:20:46,620 --> 00:20:48,873
will be "the other side" within this town.

293
00:20:50,166 --> 00:20:51,834
Come here whenever you want.

294
00:20:52,918 --> 00:20:55,670
Even if we can't get out of this town,

295
00:20:55,671 --> 00:20:58,632
I'll make sure you're never bored.

296
00:21:02,553 --> 00:21:05,598
THE FLOWERS OF EVIL

297
00:21:08,601 --> 00:21:10,728
You just sit here, Nakamura.

298
00:21:13,189 --> 00:21:14,523
That's the contract...

299
00:21:15,733 --> 00:21:16,859
I'll make with you.

300
00:21:27,453 --> 00:21:30,122
You're talking
like you've got it all figured out...

301
00:21:30,831 --> 00:21:33,042
You've got some nerve to steal mine, too.

302
00:21:34,335 --> 00:21:36,629
The only one you didn't take
was Nanako Saeki's.

303
00:21:37,213 --> 00:21:38,589
Why?

304
00:21:40,716 --> 00:21:41,759
Because...

305
00:21:42,510 --> 00:21:44,804
that's the worst thing I could do.

306
00:22:00,277 --> 00:22:02,154
[♪ dramatic music playing]

307
00:22:08,160 --> 00:22:09,537
Don't be ridiculous.

308
00:22:10,913 --> 00:22:13,666
I'm letting you make a contract with me,

309
00:22:16,377 --> 00:22:18,462
you absolute pervert.

310
00:22:29,515 --> 00:22:30,724
Do I make myself clear?

311
00:22:33,143 --> 00:22:34,144
Yeah!

312
00:22:38,524 --> 00:22:39,941
[♪ music fades]

313
00:22:39,942 --> 00:22:40,943
[Ai] Nanako!

314
00:22:42,361 --> 00:22:45,197
[Nanako sobbing]
Ai... Sorry for calling all of a sudden.

315
00:22:45,906 --> 00:22:47,283
It's just...

316
00:22:48,617 --> 00:22:50,369
I'm a weak human being.

317
00:22:50,953 --> 00:22:53,205
[♪ closing theme music playing]

318
00:22:58,377 --> 00:23:00,588
I can't... [sniffles]

319
00:23:05,634 --> 00:23:08,429
carry it all on my own, anymore...

320
00:23:10,264 --> 00:23:12,683
TO BE CONTINUED

321
00:23:47,843 --> 00:23:48,968
ON THE NEXT EPISODE

322
00:23:48,969 --> 00:23:51,763
[narrator] Kasuga and Nakamura
make a secret plan,

323
00:23:51,764 --> 00:23:54,975
and jealousy bursts into bloom
in Saeki's heart as she finds out.

324
00:23:55,559 --> 00:23:57,352
Next, on episode six,

325
00:23:57,353 --> 00:24:01,022
Saeki's madness burns
all of Kasuga's hopes to the ground.

326
00:24:01,023 --> 00:24:02,775
Translated by Yuka Kristi
